  "description": {
    "zh": "我跟几个合作方聊了聊你之前完成的任务。他们原本是想测试 G28 步枪的，但我帮你争取到了点自由度，你可以用 SR-25 或 RSASS 这些精确射手步枪来代替。\n\n多点选择总没坏处，对吧？准备好了就出发，前往海岸线执行任务。你的枪必须装上高倍率瞄准镜，建议用 30mm 的。\n\n你应该已经不止一次去那片区域了，搞定之后就回来找我吧。",
    "en": "I talked to a few associates about one of the previous jobs you completed. They originally wanted someone to test the G28 rifle but I managed to work out something else, you can use SR-25 and RSASS marksman rifles aswell\n\nHaving multiple choices is always good, so what's it gonna be then? I hope you're ready, you'll need to head to the shoreline and take out some targets there. Your rifles need to have a riflescope on them, I suggest using 30mm ones. Shouldn't be too difficult, you've been enough times there already. Come back when you took care of it."
  },
